@wp.kernel
def expr_ixymlm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = wp.abs((0.97 - (v0 + 0.33 / v2 + 0.85)))
    v1 = (v2 * (wp.abs(v2 + 0.96) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.95)))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v1 + 0.89 + v1 + 0.93)))
    data[tid] = v0
